@startuml
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid

actor "Người dùng" as User #Yellow
boundary "TourDetailPage" as UI #Yellow
boundary "AxiosClient" as API #Yellow
control "ToursController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "TourService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "Tour" as TEnt #Yellow
entity "TourType" as TTEnt #Yellow
entity "TourImage" as TIEnt #Yellow
entity "Itinerary" as IEnt #Yellow
entity "Review" as REnt #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL" as DB #Yellow

User -> UI : 1: Click vào một tour\n(hoặc truy cập /tours/{id})
activate UI
UI -> UI : 1.1: Lấy tourId từ route params
UI -> API : 1.2: GET /api/Tours/{id}
activate API
API -> Ctrl : 1.3: Chuyển tiếp request\n(không cần JWT - public endpoint)
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> Ctrl : 1.4: Parse id từ route
Ctrl -> Svc : 1.5: GetByIdAsync(id)
activate Svc

Svc -> DB : 1.6: Tours.GetQueryable()\n.Include(t => t.TourType)\n.Include(t => t.Images)\n.Include(t => t.Itineraries\n    .OrderBy(i => i.DayNumber))\n.Include(t => t.Reviews)\n.FirstOrDefaultAsync(t => t.Id == id)
activate DB

alt 1.7: [Tour không tồn tại]
DB --> Svc : 1.7.1: null
deactivate DB
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.7.2: ApiResponse<TourResponse>.Fail(\n"Tour not found", 404)
Ctrl --> API : 1.7.3: StatusCode(404)
API --> UI : 1.7.4: Response lỗi
UI --> User : 1.7.5: Hiển thị "Tour not found"
else 1.8: [Tour tồn tại]
DB --> Svc : 1.8.1: Tour (có TourType, Images,\nItineraries, Reviews)
deactivate DB
Svc -> Svc : 1.8.2: _mapper.Map<TourResponse>(tour)\n(chuyển Tour -> TourResponse:\n  - TourTypeName từ TourType.Name\n  - Images map -> TourImageResponse\n  - Itineraries sắp xếp theo DayNumber)
Svc --> Ctrl : 1.8.3: ApiResponse<TourResponse>.Ok(data)
end

deactivate Svc
Ctrl --> API : 1.9: StatusCode(200, ApiResponse<TourResponse>)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> UI : 1.10: Response JSON (tour details)
deactivate API

UI -> UI : 1.11: Hiển thị chi tiết tour:\n- Hero image + gallery (Images)\n- Thông tin cơ bản (tên, địa điểm, giá)\n- Lịch trình chi tiết (Itineraries)\n- Mô tả, Included/Excluded\n- Form đặt tour (số người, ngày đi)

note right of UI : Gọi song song:\nGET /Reviews/tour/{id}\nđể lấy đánh giá

UI -> API : 1.12: GET /api/Reviews/tour/{tourId}
activate API
API --> Ctrl : (ReviewsController)
Ctrl --> Svc : (ReviewService)
note right of API : Luồng review riêng
API --> UI : 1.13: Response danh sách review
deactivate API

UI --> User : 1.14: Hiển thị đánh giá + form đặt tour
deactivate UI

@enduml
